abstract: Stephanie Miner, the former mayor of Syracuse, is virtually unknown to voters and has almost no chance of winning. She explained why she’s running anyway.
snippet: Stephanie Miner, the former mayor of Syracuse, is virtually unknown to voters and has almost no chance of winning. She explained why she’s running anyway.
lead_paragraph: Even Stephanie Miner admits that her campaign for governor is a moonshot.

headline_main: Will Too Much Love From Trump Be a Bad Thing for a Long Island Congressman?
headline_print_headline: On Long Island, Swell of Anti-Trump Sentiment Could Cost Congressman His Job

abstract: In just three years, Gucci’s creative director has shifted the industry’s course, altering the way the world sees value, gender and even identity.
snippet: In just three years, Gucci’s creative director has shifted the industry’s course, altering the way the world sees value, gender and even identity.
lead_paragraph: ON A BRIGHT May day, Alessandro Michele and I stand side by side at the same picture window gazing at the same patch of Lower Manhattan, but we don’t have the same view. Where I see a riot of buildings born of utility and bereft of any unifying aesthetic, he sees a story, a timeline, a testament. While I want to tidy it up somehow, he wants to let it be and breathe. To me, it’s a mess — an exciting one, but still. To him, it’s a mosaic.

abstract: Price was one out short of being able to claim the win, but he did enough over four and two-thirds innings to help Boston tie the A.L.C.S. against the Astros.
snippet: Price was one out short of being able to claim the win, but he did enough over four and two-thirds innings to help Boston tie the A.L.C.S. against the Astros.
lead_paragraph: BOSTON — According to standard baseball measurements, David Price did not pitch well on Sunday night. He gave up four runs in fewer than five innings, handed back a lead that his Boston Red Sox teammates had given him in the first inning and was removed from Game 2 of the American League Championship Series against the Houston Astros after he had allowed two batters to reach base in the top of the fifth.

abstract: The Rams and the Chiefs will try to get to 6-0, and the Steelers will look to build on last week’s momentum in a crucial division matchup.
snippet: The Rams and the Chiefs will try to get to 6-0, and the Steelers will look to build on last week’s momentum in a crucial division matchup.
lead_paragraph: A pair of teams trying to get to 6-0; an A.F.C. North contest that may have lasting implications; the Bears trying to keep a good thing going; and a league still passing the ball as if running were against the rules. Week 6 has a lot going for it, and if the first five weeks are any indication, most of the games will be close.
